<h2><CENTER><B>Welcome to the PureTec Corporation Homepage</B></CENTER></h2>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="grnbar2.jpg"></CENTER><BR>
<P>PureTec Corporation is a leading producer of medical tubing and plastic materials for the medical device industry, precision tubing for writing instruments and spray dispensers, and lawn and garden products.  The company is also a leading producer of specialty vinyl and recycled plastic materials.</P>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="grnbar2.jpg"></CENTER><BR>

<FONT SIZE=+1><B><CENTER>PureTec Corporation</CENTER></B>
<B><CENTER>65 Railroad Avenue</CENTER></B>
