</B><BR>

<B><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+1><A HREF="http://www.nasdaq.com">NASDAQ</A> trading symbol:  <A HREF="http://www.nasdaq.com/scripts/html3/fquote.idc?symname=purt">PURT</A></CENTER></B></FONT SIZE><BR>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="grnbar2.jpg"></CENTER><BR>

<P>PureTec Corporation was formed in 1995 by the merger of two established companies, the "old" Pure Tech International, Inc. and Ozite Corporation. These companies and their operating subsidiaries have been combined to form a vertically integrated manufacturer of specialty plastic products that are leaders in a number of niche markets. PureTec employs approximately 1,900 people and operates 22 manufacturing facilities worldwide.</P>

